Complete FlavorMap: interactive radar with cuisine matching

Replace ingredient drag-and-drop FlavorMap with an interactive hexagonal
radar chart where users drag points on 6 flavor axes (0-10 scale) to set
their flavor preference profile. The resulting shape fills with a gradient
fingerprint. Below the chart, 3 matching cuisines and 3 matching ingredients
are suggested based on Euclidean distance. Profile persists in localStorage.

